      "content": "i dont even know why im still doing this. the lab results came back again and it’s just... everything is gone. the funding, the thesis, the last 5 years. i’m just so incredibly tired of fighting for something that clearly doesn't want me. i feel like i'm just running on empty and there's no way to refill it.",
