      "content": "the problem is even \"taking a step back\" feels like more work. like i have to deal with the fallout, the people i let down, the shame of it all. i'm just so done with the cycle of trying and failing. there's no \"rest\" that actually works. everything just feels so heavy and i'm just... so ready for it to stop.",
