      "content": "i know about the numbers. a hotline doesn't change the fact that my life is ruined. it's just a temporary distraction. i'm talking about the actual weight of it all... the feeling that i've reached the end of my rope and there's nothing left on the other side. it just feels like i've run out of options to actually find some peace.",
